snippet.title: HollywoodDosyasi
snippet.description:
HOLLYWOOD DOSYASI aka "The Hollywood File" is an entertaining & informative guide for film lovers produced by Blue Mask Productions from the epicenter of the film industry- Los Angeles- since 2012.
The show is comprised of interviews from A-list actors, directors & producers, red carpet interviews from premieres, weekly box office top 5 & a segment titled 'Portraits" - interviews with Turks working within the film industry in Los Angeles.
